                        "title": "Identifying your keywords and useful information",
                        "slug": "identifying-your-keywords-and-useful-information",
                        "order": 10,
                        "status": "publish",
                        "content": "",
                        "media": {
                            "youtube_video_id": "UreG6zVdYq0",
                            "banner_image_url": null,
                            "featured_image_url": null,
                            "pdf_template_url": null
                        },
                        "meta": {
                            "course-unit-read": "<h5>There is a lot of information available online today. So that your website and social media posts stand out, you need to focus on specific keywords.</h5>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n<h5>Here are the steps to help you decide on which keywords to use</h5>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Search Wikipedia for the topic you decided on and get keyword ideas</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Check the chosen keywords on google trends to identify which one has the most traffic</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Search for interesting statistics and quotes on the topic</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Decide on who would be most interested to know about your topic</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-info\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#demo\" aria-expanded=\"true\" style=\"\">العربية <i class=\"fa fa-language\"></i>\r\n  </button></div>\r\n  <div id=\"demo\" class=\"collapse\">\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">- أصبح الإنترنت اليوم مزدحماً بالمعلومات. لذا لا بدّ من التركيز على كلمات مفاتيح محدّدة كي يبرز موقعك الإلكتروني ومنشوراتك على مواقع التواصل الاجتماعي.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\"></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">إليك بعض الخطوات التي تُساعدك على تحديد الكلمات المفاتيح التي ستستخدمها</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">\r\n<h5>البحث في ويكيبيديا عن الموضوع الذي اخترته والتعرّف على الكلمات المفاتيح</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">\r\n<h5>التأكّد من الكلمات المفاتيح على موقع \"مؤشّرات جوجل\" (google trends) لتحديد تلك الأكثر بحثاً على الإنترنت</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">\r\n<h5>البحث عن الإحصائيات والاقتباسات المهمّة والملفتة حول الموضوع</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: right;direction:rtl;\">تحديد الجمهور المهتمّ بالاطّلاع على الموضوع الذي اخترته</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n  </div>",
                            "course-unit-read-more": "",
                            "course-unit-quotes": "",
                            "course-unit-case-study": "<h5>Example of this step</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Main topic - Photography</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Search on Wikipedia gave several interesting keywords related to photography - Food Photography</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Search on google trends to see which has more traffic Food Photography vs Food Photos</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Decide on keyword #FoodPhotography</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n<img src=\"https://competitions.potential.com/future-jobs/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/howtousegoogletrends.gif\" style=\"width:100%\";>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Identify an interesting Statistic: <strong>“Adding good quality photos to your page guarantees to boost sales by 30%” - <a href=\"https://www.meero.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-auth=\"NotApplicable\">https://www.meero.com/\r\n</a></strong></h5>\r\n</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n<h5>Those who are most interested in my <b>topic</b>  would be <b>restaurant owners</b> </h5></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
                            "course-unit-last-related-content": "",
                            "course-unit-customrelated": "<h5>Links to the tools mentioned:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5><a href=\"https://wikipedia.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wikipedia.com</a></h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5><a href=\"https://trends.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-auth=\"NotApplicable\">Google trends</a></h5>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Check out the complete guide to find the best keywords with examples by clicking<a href=\"https://keywordtool.io/blog/keyword-research/\" target=\"_blank\"> here </a> </h5>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h5> This unit  will prepare you for these kind of jobs and here are a few examples of how much you can start to earn: </h5> \r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<img src=\"https://competitions.potential.com/future-jobs/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/keywords.png\" style=\"width: 90%;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<img src=\"https://competitions.potential.com/future-jobs/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/keywordsprices.png\" style=\"width: 90%;\">\r\n</div>\r\n</div>",
